This is a 24-volt solar panel. Unfortunately, the sun is too low (and there's a tree blocking it), so the voltage dropped significantly as soon as I added a load.
It seems I'll have to wait until tomorrow to know if this solar panel is sufficient or if I need the better-performing one I ordered.
The information on Amazon indicates that this solar panel was bought in 2021, with a maximum output power of 12V 1.2A.
